
    THE BOY and his dad had just left the block of flats where
they had been enjoying a New Year’s party when death literally fell out of the
sky.A 39-year-old man named Yevgeny had just at that second
leapt from his flat on the eighth floor, apparently with the intention of
killing himself.Yevgeny succeeded in dying – but landed on the
