Mirror, this incredible tragedy happened in the town of Zaporizhia,
southern Ukraine.The unnamed boy’s mum, Anna Polishchuk, was still inside
the block of flats. By the time she discovered what had happened, paramedics
were already desperately trying to save him.Neighbour Sergey Borisov is quoted in the report as
saying: “I heard a loud thump.“Then the boy’s mother rushed out.“She ran to the ambulance where paramedics were seeking
