agonising pain in her screams.“I just couldn’t bear hearing them.”Senior paramedic Vitaly Reznikov said: “The man who
committed suicide fell right onto the boy.“The toddler crumpled from the strength of the hit.“We tried to reanimate his heart and lungs.“The boy died inside the ambulance.”Cops said they were investigating why Yevgeny committed
suicide.
